NAME
       pnmpad - add borders to portable anymap

SYNOPSIS
       pnmpad [-white|-black] [-l#] [-r#] [-t#] [-b#] [pnmfile]

DESCRIPTION
       Reads  a  portable  anymap  as  input.  Outputs a portable
       anymap with extra borders  of  the  sizes  specified.  The
       colour  of  the  borders  can  be  set  to  black or white
       (default black).


SEE ALSO
       pbmmake(1), pnmpaste(1), pbm(5)

